{"tid":2087093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［去唔去黃店好？］支持一個恐懼嘅同路人，總好過支持一個敵人","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:23:02.000Z","uid":91721,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39590f8ef9b6c3ea3499b093fb358636941cf56a","tid":2087093,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"聽日之後一定會有好多黃店撤文宣，轉為低調<br />\n<br />\n我好明白佢哋嘅恐懼，老實講，有邊個唔驚呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲要可能間鋪養緊一班手足，幾家人，壓力一定會仲大。<br />\n<br />\n所以就算撤走文宣、連儂牆都好，我都會繼續支持佢哋，講到尾，大家都只不過係普通人，驚就梗㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n而家所有嘢都要慢慢變得低調㗎啦，但係我都係會繼續幫襯黃店，慢慢陰乾班撐支共嘅柒頭。"},{"pid":"ba8384c6c23d66709ae9b346db8bdc197bfd5dfa","tid":2087093,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"Sogo 真特價！<br />\n<br />\n突發！Sogo 大特價，買$3000平$500！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ac8f68b22d726c1e04266190b768d42c90c656f","tid":2087093,"uid":244832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8fcfc1d6cb5ba6cd92737199131915f9cc5a4ccf","tid":2087093,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/x0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hva5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74Hva5.png&h=a1d38e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1df66728d3694e731c4be9bfb7d8b897841b5ce","tid":2087093,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:51:07.000Z","msg":"堅持黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceea60bf34d7eb43ff6e8225aa208823a2e14135","tid":2087093,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r